#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_4
msgid "<b>Sleeve Cut:</b>"
msgstr "<b>ການຕັດແຂນເສື້ອ:</b>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_12
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_13
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_14
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_15
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_3
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_4
msgid ""
"<b>Slim/Modern Fit:</b> Tapered through the chest and waist for a more "
"tailored look."
msgstr ""
"<b>ຊົງ Slim/Modern Fit:</b> ຊົງທີ່ເຂົ້າຮູບບໍລິເວນໜ້າເອິກ ແລະ ແອວ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ເບິ່ງເປັນຊົງທີ່ພໍດີຕົວ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Source Details:</b> Displays the product and the specific <b>\"Pick "
"From\"</b>  (the quant), including the location and the selected Lot or "
"Serial Number."
msgstr ""
"<b>ລາຍລະອຽດແຫຼ່ງທີ່ມາ:</b> ສະແດງສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ຕຳແໜ່ງ <b>\"ເກັບຈາກ\"</b> ທີ່ສະເພາະເຈາະຈົງ "
"(quant), ລວມທັງສະຖານທີ່ ແລະ ເລກລັອດ ຫຼື ຊີຣຽວທີ່ເລືອກ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Steps to adjust:</b>"
msgstr "<b>ຂັ້ນຕອນການປັບປຸງ:</b>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Storable Products:</b> Only products with \"Track Inventory\" enabled are"
" eligible."
msgstr ""
"<b>ສິນຄ້າທີ່ຈັດເກັບໄດ້:</b> ສະເພາະສິນຄ້າທີ່ເປີດໃຊ້ງານ \"ຕິດຕາມສາງ\" ເທົ່ານັ້ນທີ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>T-shirt (Finished Product)</b>: Has two variants, \"Blue\" and \"Yellow.\""
msgstr ""
"<b>ເສື້ອຢືດ (ສິນຄ້າສຳເລັດຮູບ)</b>: ມີສອງລຸ້ນຄື \"ສີຟ້າ\" ແລະ \"ສີເຫຼືອງ\""

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Tips for Changing Production Priorities: </b>If you need to change the priority on your production plan, you'll have to re-plan the entire schedule. First, select all the <b>Manufacturing Orders</b> and \"Unplan\" them.\n"
"                        Next, set the new priority (⭐) for the orders you need to adjust, then \"Re-plan\" everything. This will ensure your new priorities are reflected in the schedule."
msgstr ""
"<b>ເຄັດລັບໃນການປ່ຽນລຳດັບຄວາມສຳຄັນຂອງການຜະລິດ: </b>ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການປ່ຽນລຳດັບຄວາມສຳຄັນໃນແຜນກາ"
"ນຜະລິດ, ທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງວາງແຜນກຳນົດເວລາໃໝ່ທັງໝົດ. ທຳອິດ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກ <b>ໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດ</b> ທັງໝົດ ແລ້ວກົດ "
"\"ຍົກເລີກການວາງແຜນ (Unplan)\". ຈາກນັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ກຳນົດລຳດັບຄວາມສຳຄັນໃໝ່ (⭐) ສຳລັບໃບສັ່ງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງ"
"ການປັບປຸງ, ແລ້ວກົດ \"ວາງແຜນໃໝ່ (Re-plan)\" ທັງໝົດ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າລຳດັບຄວາມສຳຄັນໃໝ່ຂອງ"
"ທ່ານຖືກສະແດງໃນຕາຕະລາງ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Traceability Management:</b>"
msgstr "<b>ການຈັດການການຕິດຕາມ:</b>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Traceability Matching:</b> The system intelligently filters \"Convert "
"Into\" options based on tracing. For example, if you convert a Lot-tracked "
"item and provide a new Lot number, the destination product must also support"
" Lot tracking. But if you dont provide any Lot Number, only product without "
"specific traceability will be eligible for convert into."
msgstr ""
"<b>ການຈັບຄູ່ການຕິດຕາມ:</b> ລະບົບຈະກັ່ນຕອງຕົວເລືອກ \"ແປງເປັນ\" ຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບໂດຍອີງຕາມການຕິດ"
"ຕາມ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຖ້າທ່ານແປງສິນຄ້າທີ່ມີການຕິດຕາມລັອດ ແລະ ລະບຸເລກລັອດໃໝ່, ສິນຄ້າປາຍທາງກໍຕ້ອງຮອງຮັບການ"
"ຕິດຕາມລັອດນຳ. ແຕ່ຖ້າທ່ານບໍ່ລະບຸເລກລັອດ, ສະເພາະສິນຄ້າທີ່ບໍ່ມີການຕິດຕາມສະເພາະເຈາະຈົງເທົ່ານັ້ນທີ່ຈະສາມາດ"
"ແປງເປັນໄດ້."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Use the batch size setting:</b> If you always produce in batches of a "
"specific quantity, use the <b>Batch Size</b> setting in the "
"<b>Miscellaneous</b> tab."
msgstr ""
"<b>ໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂະໜາດຊຸດ (Batch size):</b> ຖ້າທ່ານຜະລິດເປັນຊຸດໃນຈຳນວນທີ່ແນ່ນອນສະເໝີ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ກາ"
"ນຕັ້ງຄ່າ <b>ຂະໜາດຊຸດ</b> ໃນແຖບ <b>ອື່ນໆ</b>."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_12
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_13
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_14
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_15
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_3
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:textile_manufacturing.product_template_4
msgid "<b>V-Neck:</b> A \"V\" shaped neckline that can be shallow or deep."
msgstr "<b>ຄໍວີ (V-Neck):</b> ຄໍເສື້ອຮູບຕົວ \"V\" ເຊິ່ງອາດຈະຕື້ນ ຫຼື ເລິກ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Variant Control &amp; Error Prevention</b>"
msgstr "<b>ການຄວບຄຸມລຸ້ນຍ່ອຍ ແລະ ການປ້ອງກັນຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ</b>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Work Center Capacity:</b> Optimize your production schedule by exploring "
"the capacity of your work centers."
msgstr ""
"<b>ກຳລັງການຜະລິດຂອງສູນວຽກ:</b> ປັບປຸງຕາຕະລາງການຜະລິດຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ມີປະສິດທິພາບ ໂດຍການກວດສອບກ"
"ຳລັງການຜະລິດຂອງສູນວຽກ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "<b>Yellow Cotton</b>: Only applies to the \"Yellow\" T-shirt variant."
msgstr "<b>Yellow Cotton</b>: ໃຊ້ກັບເສື້ອຢືດລຸ້ນສີ \"ເຫຼືອງ\" ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.homepage
msgid ""
"<br/>Our vibrant color palette is ready to brighten your wardrobe this "
"upcoming summer.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>ໂທນສີທີ່ສົດໃສຂອງພວກເຮົາພ້ອມແລ້ວທີ່ຈະມາເຕີມຄວາມສົດຊື່ນໃຫ້ກັບຕູ້ເສື້ອຜ້າຂອງທ່ານໃນລະດູຮ້ອນທີ່ກຳລັງຈະມ"
"າເຖິງນີ້.<br/>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>CRM App</b> &amp; <b>Sales App</b></font>:"
" Manage client relationships and opportunities, creating stunning quotations"
" for new collections or bulk orders."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>ແອັບ CRM</b> &amp; <b>ແອັບການຂາຍ</b></font>: "
"ຈັດການຄວາມສຳພັນກັບລູກຄ້າ ແລະ ໂອກາດ, ສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາທີ່ໜ້າປະທັບໃຈສຳລັບຄໍເລັກຊັນໃໝ່ ຫຼື ຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ຈຳນວ"
"ນຫຼາຍ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Inventory App</b>:</font> Fasten your "
"purchasing cycles and track raw materials across your warehouse and "
"subcontractor locations."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>ແອັບສາງ</b>:</font> ເລັ່ງຮອບວຽນການຈັດຊື້ ແລະ ຕິດຕາ"
"ມວັດຖຸດິບທົ່ວທັງສາງຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ສະຖານທີ່ຂອງຜູ້ຮັບເໝົາຕໍ່."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Invoicing App</b>:</font> Streamline your "
"cash flow by invoicing clients at the right time, whether upon order "
"confirmation or delivery."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>ແອັບໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້</b>:</font> ຈັດການກະແສເງິນສົດໃຫ້ຄ່ອງຕົ"
