#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"                This module is designed to streamline your daily production, from start to finish. It helps you manage customer relationships, prepare for production, purchase raw materials, and handle deliveries. With this complete solution, you\n"
"                can boost efficiency and improve customer satisfaction across all your production services.\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"                ໂມດູນນີ້ຖືກອອກແບບມາເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ການຜະລິດປະຈຳວັນຂອງທ່ານຄ່ອງຕົວ, ຕັ້ງແຕ່ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຈົນຈົ"
"ບ. ມັນຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຈັດການຄວາມສຳພັນກັບລູກຄ້າ, ກະກຽມການຜະລິດ, ຈັດຊື້ວັດຖຸດິບ ແລະ ຈັດການການຈັດສົ່ງ. ດ້ວ"
"ຍໂຊລູຊັນທີ່ສົມບູນແບບນີ້, ທ່ານ\n"
"                ສາມາດເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບ ແລະ ປັບປຸງຄວາມພໍໃຈຂອງລູກຄ້າໃນທຸກໆການບໍລິການການຜະລິດຂອ"
"ງທ່ານ.\n"
"            </span>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"                Welcome to the <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Odoo Textile Manufacturing</font></strong>!\n"
"            </span>\n"
"            <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"                ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບເຂົ້າສູ່ <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103)"
";\">Odoo Textile Manufacturing</font></strong>!\n"
"            </span>\n"
"            <br/>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"                When a purchase order for a subcontracted product is created, the system handles the entire process. As long as your Bill of Materials (BOM) is accurate, the purchase order will automatically trigger a receipt for the final product\n"
"                and a replenishment order for all necessary components.\n"
"            </span>\n"
"            <span class=\"h2-fs\"><span class=\"h2-fs\"/></span><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">\n"
"                ເມື່ອມີການສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ສຳລັບສິນຄ້າທີ່ຈ້າງນອກ (subcontracted), ລະບົບຈະຈັດການຂະ"
"ບວນການທັງໝົດ. ຕາບໃດທີ່ລາຍການວັດສະດຸ (BOM) ຂອງທ່ານຖືກຕ້ອງ, ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ຈະກະຕຸ້ນການຮັບສິນຄ້າສຳເລັດຮູບໂ"
"ດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ\n"
"                ແລະ ສ້າງໃບສັ່ງເຕີມສິນຄ້າສຳລັບສ່ວນປະກອບທີ່ຈຳເປັນທັງໝົດ.\n"
"            </span>\n"
"            <span class=\"h2-fs\"><span class=\"h2-fs\"/></span><br/>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
