#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">From the Inventory app, create your existing products."
" To automate your workflows, make sure each product is configured "
"correctly.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">ຈາກແອັບສາງ, ໃຫ້ສ້າງສິນຄ້າທີ່ມີຢູ່ຂອງທ່ານ. ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ຂັ້ນຕອນການເຮັດວຽກເປັ"
"ນອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າສິນຄ້າແຕ່ລະຢ່າງຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ.</span>"

