#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add all the <b>components</b> needed for production and adjust their "
"quantities."
msgstr ""
"ເພີ່ມ <b>ສ່ວນປະກອບ</b> ທັງໝົດທີ່ຈຳເປັນສຳລັບການຜະລິດ ແລະ ປັບຈຳນວນຂອງພວກມັນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add only the components you need to provide to the subcontractor."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມສະເພາະສ່ວນປະກອບທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງສະໜອງໃຫ້ກັບຜູ້ຮັບເໝົາຕໍ່ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Adjust the <b>Manufacturing Lead Time</b> (the time needed for production) "
"and the <b>Days to Prepare Manufacturing</b> (the time needed to replenish "
"or produce all components)."
msgstr ""
"ປັບ <b>ໄລຍະເວລາການຜະລິດ (Manufacturing Lead Time)</b> (ເວລາທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນການຜະລິດ) ແລະ "
"<b>ຈຳນວນມື້ໃນການກະກຽມການຜະລິດ</b> (ເວລາທີ່ໃຊ້ໃນການເຕີມ ຫຼື ຜະລິດສ່ວນປະກອບທັງໝົດ)."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Adjust the <b>production quantity</b> and any specific operations as needed."
msgstr "ປັບ <b>ຈຳນວນການຜະລິດ</b> ແລະ ການດຳເນີນງານສະເພາະໃດໜຶ່ງຕາມຄວາມຈຳເປັນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjust the quantity and add <b>lot numbers</b> as needed."
msgstr "ປັບຈຳນວນ ແລະ ເພີ່ມ <b>ເລກລັອດ</b> ຕາມຄວາມຈຳເປັນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model:project.tags,name:textile_manufacturing.project_tags_3
msgid "Admin"
msgstr "ແອດມິນ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"After confirming, Odoo will automatically trigger any necessary "
"replenishment if <b>reordering rules</b> are set to <b>Auto</b>. Otherwise, "
"it will be displayed on the <b>Replenishment Dashboard.</b>"
msgstr ""
"ຫຼັງຈາກຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ, Odoo ຈະກະຕຸ້ນການເຕີມສິນຄ້າທີ່ຈຳເປັນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ຫາກ <b>ກົດເກນການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນ</"
"b> ຖືກຕັ້ງເປັນ <b>ອັດຕະໂນມັດ</b>. ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ມັນຈະຖືກສະແດງຢູ່ໃນ <b>ແຜງຄວບຄຸມການເຕີມສິນຄ້າ.</"
"b>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"After these steps are complete, you can generate a new quotation directly "
"from the project, reusing the information from the design and pattern. This "
"ensures a smooth transition from the initial project phase to the final "
"sales order."
msgstr ""
"ຫຼັງຈາກຂັ້ນຕອນເຫຼົ່ານີ້ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່ໄດ້ໂດຍກົງຈາກໂຄງການ, ໂດຍນຳໃຊ້ຂໍ້ມູນຈາ"
"ກການອອກແບບ ແລະ ແມ່ແບບຄືນໃໝ່. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າການປ່ຽນຖ່າຍຈາກໄລຍະເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງໂຄງການໄປຫາໃ"
"ບສັ່ງຂາຍຂັ້ນສຸດທ້າຍເປັນໄປຢ່າງຄ່ອງຕົວ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model:product.public.category,name:textile_manufacturing.product_public_category_1
msgid "Apparel"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງນຸ່ງຫົ່ມ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.homepage
msgid "Be yourself, create your own style"
msgstr "ເປັນຕົວຂອງເຈົ້າເອງ, ສ້າງສະໄຕລ໌ຂອງເຈົ້າເອງ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Before confirming the manufacturing order, change the <b>scheduled date</b>."
" This date will serve as the deadline for replenishing all components."
msgstr ""
"ກ່ອນທີ່ຈະຢືນຢັນໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດ, ໃຫ້ປ່ຽນ <b>ວັນທີທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້</b>. ວັນທີນີ້ຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນກຳນົດເວລາໃນການເຕີມສ່ວນ"
"ປະກອບທັງໝົດ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:textile_manufacturing.product_attribute_value_12
msgid "Black"
msgstr "ສີດຳ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:textile_manufacturing.product_attribute_value_6
msgid "Blue"
msgstr "ສີນ້ຳເງິນ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:textile_manufacturing.product_attribute_value_11
msgid "Brown"
msgstr "ສີນ້ຳຕານ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By <b>configuring the warehouse and operations</b>, we can build a system tailored to your specific needs. This involves customizing all settings related to <b>storage locations, packaging, stock move types, shipping connectors</b>, and\n"
"            <b>barcode configuration</b> to ensure maximum efficiency."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍການ <b>ຕັ້ງຄ່າສາງ ແລະ ການດຳເນີນງານ</b>, ພວກເຮົາສາມາດສ້າງລະບົບທີ່ປັບໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງ"
"ການສະເພາະຂອງທ່ານ. ສິ່ງນີ້ລວມມີການປັບແຕ່ງການຕັ້ງຄ່າທັງໝົດທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບ <b>ສະຖານທີ່ຈັດເກັບ, ການຫຸ້ມຫໍ່, "
"ປະເພດການເຄື່ອນຍ້າຍສາງ, ຕົວເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ການຂົນສົ່ງ</b>, ແລະ\n"
"            <b>ການຕັ້ງຄ່າບາໂຄດ</b> ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນປະສິດທິພາບສູງສຸດ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few contacts."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍການອັບໂຫຼດຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງຂອງໂມດູນນີ້, ຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຖືກຕື່ມດ້ວຍລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ຈຳນວນໜຶ່ງແລ້ວ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Change the <b>destination location</b> if necessary."
msgstr "ປ່ຽນ <b>ສະຖານທີ່ປາຍທາງ</b> ຖ້າຈຳເປັນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Change the BOM type to <b>Subcontractor</b>."
msgstr "ປ່ຽນປະເພດ BOM ເປັນ <b>ຜູ້ຮັບເໝົາຕໍ່ (Subcontractor)</b>."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Check the <b>Chatter</b> to see how the system automatically logs the "
"quality change."
msgstr ""
"ກວດສອບທີ່ <b>Chatter</b> ເພື່ອເບິ່ງວິທີທີ່ລະບົບບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງຄຸນນະພາບໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:product.public.category,website_description:textile_manufacturing.product_public_category_6
msgid "Choose eco-friendly options that make a difference."
msgstr "ເລືອກທາງເລືອກທີ່ເປັນມິດກັບສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມເພື່ອສ້າງຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Choose the finished product you'll be receiving from your subcontractor."
msgstr "ເລືອກສິນຄ້າສຳເລັດຮູບທີ່ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຮັບຈາກຜູ້ຮັບເໝົາຕໍ່ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click <b>\"Convert.\"</b>"
msgstr "ຄລິກ <b>\"ແປງສະພາບ (Convert).\"</b>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click <b>Validate.</b>"
msgstr "ຄລິກ <b>ຢືນຢັນ (Validate).</b>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the <b>\"Allocation\"</b> button, then select the sales order or "
"delivery you want to fulfill."
msgstr ""
"ຄລິກປຸ່ມ <b>\"ການຈັດສັນ (Allocation)\"</b>, ຈາກນັ້ນເລືອກໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ ຫຼື ການຈັດສົ່ງທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເຮັ"
"ດໃຫ້ສຳເລັດ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the <b>\"Generate BOM\"</b> button. (This button is only visible if a "
"BOM has not yet been selected on the manufacturing order.)"
msgstr ""
"ຄລິກປຸ່ມ <b>\"ສ້າງ BOM\"</b>. (ປຸ່ມນີ້ຈະປາກົດໃຫ້ເຫັນກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອຍັງບໍ່ທັນມີການເລືອກ BOM ໃນໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດເທົ່າ"
"ນັ້ນ.)"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Clicking the button opens a guided pop-up containing:"
msgstr "ການຄລິກປຸ່ມຈະເປັນການເປີດປັອບອັບແນະນຳທີ່ປະກອບດ້ວຍ:"

