#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.homepage
msgid "Craftsmanship that stands out"
msgstr "ຝີມືການຜະລິດທີ່ໂດດເດັ່ນ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a new manufacturing order for the product, using the BOM you just "
"generated."
msgstr "ສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດໃໝ່ສຳລັບສິນຄ້າ ໂດຍໃຊ້ BOM ທີ່ທ່ານຫາກໍສ້າງຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Create a new manufacturing order."
msgstr "ສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດໃໝ່."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create and assign specific product categories to easily classify your "
"products."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງ ແລະ ກຳນົດໝວດໝູ່ສິນຄ້າສະເພາະເພື່ອຈັດແບ່ງປະເພດສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create project templates within the <b>Project app</b> to easily reuse for "
"similar projects."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງແມ່ແບບໂຄງການພາຍໃນ <b>ແອັບໂຄງການ</b> ເພື່ອໃຫ້ນຳມາໃຊ້ຄືນໄດ້ງ່າຍສຳລັບໂຄງການທີ່ຄ້າຍຄືກັນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create the <b>operations</b>, link them to their respective <b>work "
"centers</b>, and specify the required time for each."
msgstr ""
"ສ້າງ <b>ການດຳເນີນງານ</b>, ເຊື່ອມໂຍງພວກມັນກັບ <b>ສູນວຽກ</b> ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ ແລະ ລະບຸເວລາທີ່ຈຳເປັນ"
"ສຳລັບແຕ່ລະຢ່າງ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Create your Product Catalog 👖"
msgstr "ສ້າງລາຍການສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ 👖"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model:product.template,name:textile_manufacturing.product_template_5
msgid "Custom Shirt (ETO)"
msgstr "ເສື້ອສັ່ງເຮັດພິເສດ (ETO)"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Customers can request a quote directly from your website's contact form. You"
" can then follow up with them in the <b>CRM app</b> to clarify their needs "
