msgid "Magenta"
msgstr "ສີມ່ວງແດງ (Magenta)"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.contactus
msgid "My Company"
msgstr "ບໍລິສັດຂອງຂ້ອຍ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Navigate to the <b>Bill of Material</b> section and create a new BOM."
msgstr "ໄປທີ່ສ່ວນ <b>ລາຍການວັດສະດຸ (BOM)</b> ແລະ ສ້າງ BOM ໃໝ່."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Navigate to the Bill of Materials section and create a new one."
msgstr "ໄປທີ່ສ່ວນລາຍການວັດສະດຸ ແລະ ສ້າງອັນໃໝ່."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to <b>manage your "
"entire business from your phone</b>.<s><br/></s>"
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຖືກລວມເຂົ້າໃນແອັບຢ່າງສົມບູນ. ດາວໂຫຼດມັນເພື່ອ <b>ຈັດການທຸລະກິດທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານຈາກໂທລະສັບ</b>"
".<s><br/></s>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo will help you adapt your website to fit your clients' needs perfectly. "
"Easily integrate your internal policies, customize the contact form, "
"showcase your latest products, and much more!"
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຈະຊ່ວຍທ່ານປັບປຸງເວັບໄຊໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງລູກຄ້າຢ່າງສົມບູນແບບ. ເຊື່ອມໂຍງນະໂຍບາຍພາ"
"ຍໃນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ, ປັບແຕ່ງແບບຟອມຕິດຕໍ່, ສະແດງສິນຄ້າຫຼ້າສຸດ ແລະ ອື່ນໆອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ!"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນວ່າ ນີ້ເປັນພຽງພາບລວມຂອງຟີເຈີທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນແພັກເກດນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລຶບ ຫຼື ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ "
"ແລະ ທົດລອງທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ຕາມຕ້ອງການ!"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"On the finished product's settings, you'll need to add the subcontractor to "
"the <b>vendor list</b>. Be sure to include the price you'll pay for their "
"subcontracting service."
msgstr ""
"ໃນການຕັ້ງຄ່າສິນຄ້າສຳເລັດຮູບ, ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງເພີ່ມຜູ້ຮັບເໝົາຕໍ່ເຂົ້າໃນ <b>ລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ສະໜອງ</b>. ໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າໄ"
"ດ້ລະບຸລາຄາທີ່ທ່ານຈະຈ່າຍສຳລັບການບໍລິການຈ້າງນອກຂອງພວກເຂົາ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once clicking on \"Convert\" button an <b>Automated Manufacturing Order "
"(MO)</b> is executed in the background:"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອຄລິກທີ່ປຸ່ມ \"ແປງສະພາບ (Convert)\", <b>ໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດ (MO) ອັດຕະໂນມັດ</b> ຈະຖືກດຳເນີນການໃ"
"ນເບື້ອງຫຼັງ:"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once production is planned, workers can execute and monitor their tasks using the <b>Shop Floor App</b>. This app can be installed as a standalone application. It's designed to be used by multiple employees on a single device, with each\n"
"            employee registering their work individually."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອມີການວາງແຜນການຜະລິດແລ້ວ, ພະນັກງານສາມາດດຳເນີນການ ແລະ ຕິດຕາມວຽກຂອງພວກເຂົາໄດ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ "
"<b>ແອັບ Shop Floor</b>. ແອັບນີ້ສາມາດຕິດຕັ້ງເປັນແອັບພລິເຄຊັນແຍກຕ່າງຫາກໄດ້. ມັນຖືກອອກແບບມາເພື່ອໃ"
"ຫ້ພະນັກງານຫຼາຍຄົນໃຊ້ໃນອຸປະກອນດຽວກັນ, ໂດຍທີ່ແຕ່ລະ\n"
"            ຄົນຈະບັນທຶກການເຮັດວຽກຂອງຕົນເອງແຍກກັນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once production orders are confirmed, they need to be planned. The scheduled"
" date on the <b>Manufacturing Order (MO)</b> is just an initial estimate and"
" doesn't consider your actual capacity."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດຖືກຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ, ພວກມັນຈະຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການວາງແຜນ. ວັນທີທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນ <b>ໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດ (MO)"
"</b> ເປັນພຽງການຄາດຄະເນເບື້ອງຕົ້ນ ແລະ ບໍ່ໄດ້ຄຳນຶງເຖິງກຳລັງການຜະລິດທີ່ແທ້ຈິງຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the client approves the pattern, you can send the quote with the final "
"product and price. This time, the delivery will be created directly from the"
" <b>Sales Order</b>."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອລູກຄ້າອະນຸມັດແມ່ແບບແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດສົ່ງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາພ້ອມກັບສິນຄ້າສຳເລັດຮູບ ແລະ ລາຄາຂັ້ນສຸດທ້າຍ. ຄັ້"
"ງນີ້, ການຈັດສົ່ງຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍກົງຈາກ <b>ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ</b>."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Once their requirements are clear, you have two possible workflows:"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງພວກເຂົາຊັດເຈນແລ້ວ, ທ່ານມີສອງຂັ້ນຕອນການເຮັດວຽກທີ່ເປັນໄປໄດ້:"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once you've created a purchase order, validate it in the <b>Purchase "
"app</b>. This powerful app allows you to group orders, compare different "
"supplier offers, track receipt accuracy, and more."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທ່ານສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຊື້ແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ຢືນຢັນມັນໃນ <b>ແອັບການຈັດຊື້</b>. ແອັບທີ່ຊົງພະລັງນີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດກຸ່ມຄ"
