" are available, it's best to start with a simple process and add new "
"features only after you've had time to test them."
msgstr ""
"ໂມດູນ <b>ສາງ</b> ຂອງ Odoo ນັ້ນຊົງພະລັງຫຼາຍ. ເຖິງວ່າຈະມີຟີເຈີດີໆຫຼາຍຢ່າງ, ແຕ່ມັນດີທີ່ສຸດທີ່ຈະເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວ"
"ຍຂະບວນການງ່າຍໆ ແລະ ຄ່ອຍເພີ່ມຟີເຈີໃໝ່ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ທ່ານມີເວລາທົດລອງໃຊ້ພວກມັນແລ້ວ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Replenishment view gives you a clear overview of all current and future needs (you can adjust the <b>Horizon settings</b> to see what's coming up). From this screen, you can directly create purchase orders, subcontracting orders, or\n"
"            manufacturing orders."
msgstr ""
"ມຸມມອງການເຕີມສິນຄ້າຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານເຫັນພາບລວມທີ່ຊັດເຈນຂອງຄວາມຕ້ອງການໃນປະຈຸບັນ ແລະ ອະນາຄົດທັງໝົດ (ທ່າ"
"ນສາມາດປັບ <b>ການຕັ້ງຄ່າໄລຍະເວລາ</b> ເພື່ອເບິ່ງສິ່ງທີ່ຈະມາເຖິງ). ຈາກໜ້າຈໍນີ້, ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງໃບສັ່ງ"
"ຊື້, ໃບສັ່ງຈ້າງນອກ ຫຼື\n"
"            ໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດໄດ້ໂດຍກົງ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The barcode app can be installed as a standalone application on devices. "
"This means people can use it without having access to the rest of the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບບາໂຄດສາມາດຕິດຕັ້ງເປັນແອັບພລິເຄຊັນແຍກຕ່າງຫາກໃນອຸປະກອນຕ່າງໆໄດ້. ນັ້ນໝາຍຄວາມວ່າພະນັກງານສາມາດ"
"ໃຊ້ມັນໄດ້ໂດຍທີ່ບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງເຂົ້າເຖິງສ່ວນອື່ນໆຂອງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "The customer reminders."
msgstr "ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The delivery for these orders will be created automatically from the "
"<b>Sales Order</b>."
msgstr ""
"ການຈັດສົ່ງສຳລັບໃບສັ່ງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດຈາກ <b>ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ</b>."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "The financial reporting."
msgstr "ລາຍງານທາງການເງິນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The process for creating a production order is similar for both <b>Engineer-to-Order (ETO)</b> and <b>Make-to-Order (MTO)</b> products. To allow for greater flexibility in choosing the correct <b>Bill of Materials (BOM)</b> and making\n"
"            any needed adjustments, you must manually create a manufacturing order after a sales order is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"ຂະບວນການສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດແມ່ນຄ້າຍຄືກັນສຳລັບທັງສິນຄ້າແບບ <b>ອອກແບບຕາມສັ່ງ (ETO)</b> ແລະ <b>ຜະລິ"
"ດເມື່ອມີຄຳສັ່ງ (MTO)</b>. ເພື່ອໃຫ້ມີຄວາມຢືດຢຸ່ນຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນໃນການເລືອກ <b>ລາຍການວັດສະດຸ (BOM)</b> ທີ່ຖື"
"ກຕ້ອງ ແລະ ການ\n"
"            ປັບປຸງທີ່ຈຳເປັນ, ທ່ານຕ້ອງສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດດ້ວຍຕົນເອງຫຼັງຈາກໃບສັ່ງຂາຍຖືກຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The production process is identical until the final customization step."
msgstr "ຂະບວນການຜະລິດແມ່ນຄືກັນທຸກປະການຈົນເຖິງຂັ້ນຕອນການປັບແຕ່ງຂັ້ນສຸດທ້າຍ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "The synchronisation with the banks."
msgstr "ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັບທະນາຄານ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "The vendor bills payment."
msgstr "ການຊຳລະໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ຜູ້ສະໜອງ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This flexibility allows you to manage different production processes for the"
" same product, making it easy to use existing inventory when possible."
msgstr ""
"ຄວາມຢືດຢຸ່ນນີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຈັດການຂະບວນການຜະລິດທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນສຳລັບສິນຄ້າດຽວກັນ, ເຮັດໃຫ້ງ່າຍໃນການນຳໃຊ້ເຄື່"
"ອງທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນສາງເມື່ອສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Tips for success:"
msgstr "ເຄັດລັບສູ່ຄວາມສຳເລັດ:"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To create a new Bill of Materials from scratch, you'll need to know that there are two distinct types: <b>Production BOMs</b> (for in-house production) and <b>Subcontracting BOMs</b> (for external production). Each type requires\n"
"            different settings."
msgstr ""
"ໃນການສ້າງລາຍການວັດສະດຸ (BOM) ໃໝ່ຕັ້ງແຕ່ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, ທ່ານຕ້ອງຮູ້ວ່າມີສອງປະເພດທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນຄື: <b>BOM ກ"
"ານຜະລິດ</b> (ສຳລັບການຜະລິດພາຍໃນ) ແລະ <b>BOM ການຈ້າງນອກ</b> (ສຳລັບການຜະລິດພາຍນອກ). ແ"
"ຕ່ລະປະເພດຕ້ອງການ\n"
"            ການຕັ້ງຄ່າທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model:project.task.type,name:textile_manufacturing.project_task_type_11
msgid "To do"
msgstr "ສິ່ງທີ່ຈະຕ້ອງເຮັດ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To get a rapid understanding of the processes this Odoo package offers, you "
"can execute the following flows and configure the settings to suit your "
"production."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອໃຫ້ເຂົ້າໃຈຂະບວນການທີ່ແພັກເກດ Odoo ນີ້ສະເໜີໃຫ້ຢ່າງວ່ອງໄວ, ທ່ານສາມາດດຳເນີນການຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ "
"ແລະ ຕັ້ງຄ່າໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບການຜະລິດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "To get started:"
msgstr "ເພື່ອເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ:"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To include all the necessary information, such as the logo to be printed, "
"technical measurements, and other details, you can choose one of two "
"methods:"
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອລວມເອົາຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈຳເປັນທັງໝົດ ເຊັ່ນ: ໂລໂກ້ທີ່ຈະພິມ, ການວັດແທກທາງເຕັກນິກ ແລະ ລາຍລະອຽດອື່ນໆ, ທ່ານສ"
"າມາດເລືອກໜຶ່ງໃນສອງວິທີ:"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "To make your workflow even more efficient, explore these features:"
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອໃຫ້ຂັ້ນຕອນການເຮັດວຽກຂອງທ່ານມີປະສິດທິພາບຍິ່ງຂຶ້ນ, ໃຫ້ສຶກສາຟີເຈີເຫຼົ່ານີ້:"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To plan your orders, go to the manufacturing app, select them, and click \"Plan.\" The system will then generate a detailed schedule that accounts for the capacity of your <b>work centers</b>. You can see a clear overview of your schedule\n"
"            on the planning by work centers screen."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອວາງແຜນໃບສັ່ງຂອງທ່ານ, ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ແອັບການຜະລິດ, ເລືອກພວກມັນ, ແລ້ວຄລິກ \"ວາງແຜນ (Plan).\" ຈາ"
"ກນັ້ນລະບົບຈະສ້າງຕາຕະລາງລາຍລະອຽດທີ່ຄຳນຶງເຖິງກຳລັງການຜະລິດຂອງ <b>ສູນວຽກ</b> ຂອງທ່ານ. ທ່ານສາມ"
"າດເຫັນພາບລວມທີ່ຊັດເຈນຂອງຕາຕະລາງ\n"
"            ໃນໜ້າຈໍການວາງແຜນຕາມສູນວຽກ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To provide maximum flexibility during warehouse operations, a new Convert "
"button is now available on transfer from the backend and from the barcode "
"app."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອໃຫ້ມີຄວາມຢືດຢຸ່ນສູງສຸດໃນລະຫວ່າງການດຳເນີນງານສາງ, ຕອນນີ້ມີປຸ່ມແປງສະພາບ (Convert) ໃໝ່ໃນການໂອ"
"ນຍ້າຍຈາກທັງເບື້ອງຫຼັງ (backend) ແລະ ຈາກແອັບບາໂຄດ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.homepage
msgid "Transform your closet with our fresh designs"
msgstr "ປ່ຽນໂສມຕູ້ເສື້ອຜ້າຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍການອອກແບບໃໝ່ໆຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.homepage
msgid "Unveil Our Newest Clothing Line"
msgstr "ເປີດຕົວສາຍຜະລິດຕະພັນເສື້ອຜ້າໃໝ່ຫຼ້າສຸດຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use barcode scanners to validate stock movements, identify pallet positions,"
" and perform fast, accurate stock operations. Greatly improves warehouse "
"efficiency and reduces human error."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງສະແກນບາໂຄດເພື່ອຢືນຢັນການເຄື່ອນຍ້າຍສາງ, ລະບຸຕຳແໜ່ງພາເລັດ ແລະ ດຳເນີນການສາງໄດ້ຢ່າງວ່ອງໄ"
"ວ ແລະ ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ຊ່ວຍປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບຂອງສາງຢ່າງຫຼວງຫຼາຍ ແລະ ຫຼຸດຜ່ອນຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຈາກຄົນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <b>PLM app</b> to review and update your Bills of Material (BOMs) at"
" the right time."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <b>ແອັບ PLM</b> ເພື່ອກວດສອບ ແລະ ອັບເດດລາຍການວັດສະດຸ (BOM) ຂອງທ່ານໃນເວລາທີ່ເໝາະສົມ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Use the <strong>Accounting</strong> app to easily handle:"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ແອັບ <strong>ບັນຊີ</strong> ເພື່ອຈັດການສິ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ:"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Uses a consistent and repeatable production process."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຂະບວນການຜະລິດທີ່ຄົງທີ່ ແລະ ສາມາດເຮັດຊ້ຳໄດ້."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Utilizes a <b>standard BOM</b> with options for small <b>customization</b>."
msgstr "ນຳໃຊ້ <b>BOM ມາດຕະຖານ</b> ພ້ອມຕົວເລືອກໃນການ <b>ປັບແຕ່ງ</b> ເລັກນ້ອຍ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:textile_manufacturing.product_attribute_value_8
msgid "Violet"
msgstr "ສີມ່ວງ (Violet)"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model:project.project.stage,name:textile_manufacturing.project_project_stage_5
msgid "Waiting client validation"
msgstr "ກຳລັງລໍຖ້າການຢືນຢັນຈາກລູກຄ້າ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"We’ve set up a <b>\"Polo with Quality Level\"</b> product to demonstrate "
"this process. Open delivery <b>WH/OUT/00002</b> (Red Polo). Imagine 20 of "
"the 40 units were water-damaged in storage and cannot be sold as Premium "
"stock."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າສິນຄ້າ <b>\"ເສື້ອໂປໂລພ້ອມລະດັບຄຸນນະພາບ\"</b> ເພື່ອສາທິດຂະບວນການນີ້. ໃຫ້ເປີດໃບຈັດ"
"ສົ່ງ <b>WH/OUT/00002</b> (ເສື້ອໂປໂລສີແດງ). ສົມມຸດວ່າ 20 ຈາກ 40 ໜ່ວຍໄດ້ຮັບຄວາມເສຍຫາຍຈາກນ້ຳ"
"ໃນລະຫວ່າງການຈັດເກັບ ແລະ ບໍ່ສາມາດຂາຍເປັນສິນຄ້າລະດັບພຣີມຽມໄດ້."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When you create a manufacturing order for a specific variant, such as a \"Yellow\" T-shirt, the system automatically pulls only the necessary materials—in this case, the <b>Yellow Cotton</b> and the <b>Clothing Label</b>. This approach\n"
"            helps streamline the production process and ensures you only use the components needed for each specific version of the product."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທ່ານສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດສຳລັບລຸ້ນສະເພາະ ເຊັ່ນ: ເສື້ອຢືດ \"ສີເຫຼືອງ\", ລະບົບຈະດຶງສະເພາະວັດສະດຸທີ່ຈຳເປັນ"
"ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ—ໃນກໍລະນີນີ້ແມ່ນ <b>ຜ້າຝ້າຍສີເຫຼືອງ</b> ແລະ <b>ປ້າຍເສື້ອ</b>. ວິທີນີ້\n"
"            ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຂະບວນການຜະລິດຄ່ອງຕົວ ແລະ ຮັບປະກັນວ່າທ່ານຈະໃຊ້ສະເພາະສ່ວນປະກອບທີ່ຈຳເປັນສຳລັ"
"ບແຕ່ລະເວີຊັນຂອງສິນຄ້າເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "When you're ready to manage a transfer:"
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານພ້ອມທີ່ຈະຈັດການການໂອນຍ້າຍ:"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When you're ready, create a <b>Manufacturing Order</b> specifically for the "
"pattern and initiate production (don't link a Bill of Materials (BOM) for "
"this one, as it doesn't have one)"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທ່ານພ້ອມແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ສ້າງ <b>ໃບສັ່ງຜະລິດ</b> ສຳລັບແມ່ແບບໂດຍສະເພາະ ແລະ ເລີ່ມການຜະລິດ (ບໍ່ຕ້ອງເຊື່"
"ອມໂຍງ BOM ສຳລັບໃບສັ່ງນີ້ ເພາະວ່າມັນຍັງບໍ່ທັນມີ)"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When you're ready, you have the flexibility to create an invoice for either "
"a full or a partial payment, such as a down payment. All invoices generated "
"are tracked and can be managed through the <b>Invoices app</b>."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທ່ານພ້ອມແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ສຳລັບການຊຳລະເຕັມຈຳນວນ ຫຼື ບາງສ່ວນໄດ້ ເຊັ່ນ: ເງິນມັດຈຳ. ໃ"
"ບແຈ້ງໜີ້ທັງໝົດທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນຈະຖືກຕິດຕາມ ແລະ ສາມາດຈັດການໄດ້ຜ່ານ <b>ແອັບໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້</b>."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While the system allows broad product-to-product conversion, you can enforce"
" strict rules using the <b>\"Convert Attribute\"</b> setting:"
msgstr ""
"ເຖິງວ່າລະບົບຈະອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ມີການແປງສະພາບສິນຄ້າຢ່າງກວ້າງຂວາງ, ແຕ່ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດກົດເກນທີ່ເຂັ້ມງວດໄດ້ໂ"
"ດຍໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ <b>\"ຄຸນລັກສະນະການແປງສະພາບ (Convert Attribute)\"</b>:"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While you can manually move an operation with a simple drag and drop, keep "
"in mind this change is isolated to that specific work order and will not re-"
"plan the others."
msgstr ""
"ເຖິງວ່າທ່ານສາມາດຍ້າຍການດຳເນີນງານໄດ້ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງໂດຍການລາກ ແລະ ວາງ, ແຕ່ໃຫ້ຈື່ໄວ້ວ່າການປ່ຽນແປງນີ້ຈະ"
"ມີຜົນສະເພາະກັບໃບສັ່ງວຽກນັ້ນເທົ່ານັ້ນ ແລະ ຈະບໍ່ມີການວາງແຜນໃໝ່ສຳລັບໃບສັ່ງອື່ນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:textile_manufacturing.product_attribute_value_13
msgid "White"
msgstr "ສີຂາວ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Within the <strong>Inventory App</strong>"
msgstr "ພາຍໃນ <strong>ແອັບສາງ</strong>"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Working with Bill of Materials (BOM) variants is a great way to automate the"
" replenishment of specific components. However, this approach can add "
"complexity and make it difficult to simplify your product structure later "
"on."
msgstr ""
"ການເຮັດວຽກກັບລຸ້ນຍ່ອຍຂອງລາຍການວັດສະດຸ (BOM) ເປັນວິທີທີ່ດີໃນການເຮັດໃຫ້ການເຕີມສ່ວນປະກອບສະເພາະເປັນ"
"ອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ແນວໃດກໍຕາມ, ວິທີນີ້ອາດຈະເພີ່ມຄວາມຊັບຊ້ອນ ແລະ ເຮັດໃຫ້ການປັບໂຄງສ້າງສິນຄ້າໃຫ້ງ່າຍຂຶ້ນໃນພາ"
"ຍຫຼັງເປັນເລື່ອງຍາກ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປຶກສາກ່ຽວກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Odoo ກັບພວກເຮົາ ຫຼື ສຶກສາເພີ່ມເຕີມບໍ່?"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:textile_manufacturing.product_attribute_value_4
msgid "Yellow"
msgstr "ສີເຫຼືອງ"

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You also have the flexibility to invoice for these services at any point, or"
" even include them for free if the client agrees to the final quote."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ສຳລັບການບໍລິການເຫຼົ່ານີ້ໄດ້ທຸກເວລາ, ຫຼື ແມ່ນແຕ່ລວມໃຫ້ຟຣີຫາກລູກຄ້າຕົກລົງຕາມໃບສະ"
"ເໜີລາຄາຂັ້ນສຸດທ້າຍ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ທີ່ແຜງຄວບຄຸມຫຼັກ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can assign one or more employees to each operation. This makes them "
"visible on the planning schedule and links the operations to the correct "
"workers in the shop floor app."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດມອບໝາຍພະນັກງານໜຶ່ງຄົນ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍຄົນໃຫ້ກັບແຕ່ລະການດຳເນີນງານ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ພວກເຂົາປາກົດໃນຕ"
"າຕະລາງການວາງແຜນ ແລະ ເຊື່ອມໂຍງການດຳເນີນງານກັບພະນັກງານທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງໃນແອັບ shop floor."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can choose to charge a standard price for your design work or track the "
"time spent and bill the client later."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກທີ່ຈະຄິດລາຄາມາດຕະຖານສຳລັບວຽກອອກແບບຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ຕິດຕາມເວລາທີ່ໃຊ້ແລ້ວຄ່ອຍອອກໃບແຈ້ງ"
"ໜີ້ໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າໃນພາຍຫຼັງ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can create multiple Bills of Materials (BOMs) for the same finished "
"product. This is useful for products that can be made in different ways."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງລາຍການວັດສະດຸ (BOM) ຫຼາຍລາຍການສຳລັບສິນຄ້າສຳເລັດຮູບດຽວກັນ. ສິ່ງນີ້ມີປະໂຫຍດສຳລັບສິນຄ້"
"າທີ່ສາມາດຜະລິດໄດ້ດ້ວຍຫຼາຍວິທີ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can customize the settings for each operation type within the barcode application to control what is permitted during the process. This allows you to define specific rules for operations like picking, ensuring the\n"
"                        barcode functionality aligns with your business workflow."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດປັບແຕ່ງການຕັ້ງຄ່າສຳລັບແຕ່ລະປະເພດການດຳເນີນງານພາຍໃນແອັບພລິເຄຊັນບາໂຄດ ເພື່ອຄວບຄຸມສິ່ງທີ່ໄດ້"
"ຮັບອະນຸຍາດໃນລະຫວ່າງຂະບວນການ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານກຳນົດກົດເກນສະເພາະສຳລັບການດຳເນີນງານ ເຊັ່ນ: ການເ"
"ກັບເຄື່ອງ, ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນວ່າ\n"
"                        ການເຮັດວຽກຂອງບາໂຄດສອດຄ່ອງກັບຂັ້ນຕອນການເຮັດວຽກຂອງທຸລະກິດຂອງທ່າ"
"ນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can easily invoice clients directly from a <b>Sales Order</b>. Each "
"order allows you to set specific <b>payment terms and conditions</b> "
"tailored to that client or project."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າໄດ້ໂດຍກົງຈາກ <b>ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ</b>. ແຕ່ລະໃບສັ່ງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານກຳນົດ <b>ເງື່ອ"
"ນໄຂການຊຳລະເງິນ</b> ສະເພາະທີ່ປັບໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບລູກຄ້າ ຫຼື ໂຄງການນັ້ນ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can print <b>barcode commands</b> to streamline your operations with "
"quick scanning actions."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດພິມ <b>ຄຳສັ່ງບາໂຄດ</b> ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ການດຳເນີນງານຂອງທ່ານຄ່ອງຕົວດ້ວຍການສະແກນທີ່ວ່ອງໄວ."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries"
" &gt; Upgrade your Textile Manufacturing package and select the relevant "
"checkbox"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງບໍ່? ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້. ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ ແອັບ &gt; ອຸດສາຫະກຳ &gt; ອັບເກຣດແພັກ"
"ເກດ Textile Manufacturing ຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ເລືອກຊ່ອງໝາຍທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ"

